        <div data-component-type="quote">
            <p class="quote-text"><q class="show-quotes">Our homes have become our ‘cocoon’ - a safe haven. We want to be very careful every time we step out of our ‘cocoon’ or allow anything into it, so we’re very sensible about where we shop, how we shop and when we shop.</q></p>
            
            <p class="post-quote quote-author">Ashok Vaswani</p>
            <p class="post-quote">Chief Executive Officer of Consumer Banking and Payments</p>
